#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:16
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kappname; editor is the editing area of the &kappname; window. This "
"editor is shared between &kate; and &kwrite;, and it can also be used in "
"&konqueror; for displaying text files from your local computer, or from the "
"network."
msgstr ""
"&kate; Muhinduzi ni i Guhindura Umwanya Bya i &kate; Idirishya . Muhinduzi "
"ni Byakoreshejwe ku &kwrite; , na Byakoreshejwe in &konqueror; ya:  "
"Umwandiko Idosiye Kuva: Bya hafi , Cyangwa Kuva: i urusobe . "

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:21
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "The editor is composed of the following components:"
msgstr "Muhinduzi ni Bya i : "

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:26
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "The editing area"
msgstr "Guhindura Umwanya "

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:27
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "This is where the text of your document is located."
msgstr "ni i Umwandiko Bya Inyandiko ni . "

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:31
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "The Scrollbars"
msgstr "Imirongo-ntambike "

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:33
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The scrollbars indicate the position of the visible part of the document "
"text, and can be used to move around the document. Dragging the scrollbars "
"will not cause the insertion cursor to be moved."
msgstr ""
"Imirongo-ntambike i Ibirindiro: Bya i Kigaragara Inzira %s Bya i Inyandiko "
"Umwandiko , na Byakoreshejwe Kuri Himura i Inyandiko . i Udufashagenda OYA i "
"Iyinjizamo indanga Kuri . "

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:37
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "The scrollbars are displayed and hidden as required."
msgstr "Imirongo-ntambike na Birahishe Nka Bya ngombwa . "

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:42
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "The Icon Border"
msgstr "Kwerekana Impera z'Agashushondanga"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:44
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The icon border is a small pane on the left side of the editor, displaying a "
"small icon next to marked lines."
msgstr ""
"Agashushondanga Impera: ni A Gitoya ku i Ibumoso: Bya i Muhinduzi , A Gitoya "
"Agashushondanga Ibikurikira > Kuri cy/byagarajwe Imirongo . "

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:46
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can set or remove a <link linkend=\"kate-part-bookmarks\">bookmark</"
"link> in a visible line by clicking the &LMB; in the icon border next to "
"that line."
msgstr ""
"Gushyiraho Cyangwa Gukuraho A <link linkend=\"kate-part-bookmarks\"> "
"Akamenyetso </link> in A Kigaragara Umurongo: ku i &LMB; in i "
"Agashushondanga Impera: Ibikurikira > Kuri Umurongo: . "

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:49
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The display of the icon border can be toggled using the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Icon Border</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Kugaragaza: Bya i Agashushondanga Impera: ikoresha i <menuchoice> <guimenu> "
"</guimenu> <guimenuitem> </guimenuitem> </menuchoice> Ibikubiyemo Ikintu . "

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:56
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "The Line Numbers Pane"
msgstr "Gushiraho ibaramirongo"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:58
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Line numbers pane shows the line numbers of all visible lines in the "
"document."
msgstr ""
"Imibare i Umurongo: Imibare Bya Byose Kigaragara Imirongo in i Inyandiko . "

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:60
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The display of the Line Numbers Pane can be toggled using the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Line Numbers</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Kugaragaza: Bya i ikoresha i <menuchoice> <guimenu> </guimenu> <guimenuitem> "
"</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> Ibikubiyemo Ikintu . "

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:67
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "The Folding Pane"
msgstr "Guhindura Umwanya "

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The folding pane allows you to collapse or expand foldable blocks of lines. "
"The calculation of the foldable regions is done according to rules in the "
"syntax highlight definition for the document."
msgstr ""

