msgstr ""
"Gukoporora Umwandiko , Guhitamo na Koresha i <menuchoice> <guimenu> </"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem> </guimenuitem> </menuchoice> Ibikubiyemo Ikintu . , "
"Umwandiko Na: i Imbeba Byahiswemo Umwandiko Kuri Kuri i Ububikokoporora . "

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:251
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To paste the text currently in the clipboard, use the <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu "
"item."
msgstr ""
"Komeka i Umwandiko in i Ububikokoporora , Koresha i <menuchoice> <guimenu> </"
